itunes:title: Being The Bread Winners & How It Affects Our Relationships | Ep 6
title: Being The Bread Winners & How It Affects Our Relationships | Ep 6
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description:
How do you let the man in your life be the man when you're so used to being in control of everything in the day to day of your business? How do you balance feminine and masculine energy in your relationship when you're so used to being "in charge"? How does that affect your relationship or even just friendships? What do you do about it?? In today's episode we talk all about being entrepreneurs and the breadwinners and how that affects our relationships. We also chat about balancing our work pants and home life (aka balancing your feminine and masculine energy), which is very difficult!!

We're also on youtube! https://youtu.be/vSQ7s3R0hYk
